 days - more or less - you had your places done up and it was all distempered, you never - hardly had wallpaper on the walls, there was - but used to look very nice, pale blue -
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1310935 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12611241\charrsid13308020 Who would do that?
