Oh yes, he - we all used to sit round - of a night time when he had - when he was at home, and he'd read us all - tell us stories and read out the book to us, oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1310935 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12611241\charrsid13308020 What sort of stories?
