\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1310935 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12611241\charrsid13308020 Were you expected to go to bed at a certain time where you were at school?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10319924 MN  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12611241\charrsid13308020 
Well - no, not actually, it was mostly - as we got older we went - got - went to bed about ten o'clock. But - of course - we used to go to bed when we were tired if we was tired at seven, eight or nine we'd go to bed any time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1310935 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12611241\charrsid13308020 Did your mother or anyone else put you to bed?
