air - for the men that had lost their hair during the war that I had it off. And so we - rolled it up and I took it in and they sent it off to this place. I never had no name and address. And she said, that'll make a lovely - head of hair for - for somebo
dy you know and that. And that's how I come to get me hair off. Funny story that isn't it?
