o the Girls - to the girls club, then, you know and that and we used to - have dances and we used to have sort of games you know and that there, and that belonged to Stepney church then. I used to go there, to this - hall we used to go.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1310935 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid12611241\charrsid13308020 How many times a week would you do that?
